{"type":"message","id":"471a2abd","parentId":"49edb26f","timestamp":"2026-03-19T00:06:48.788Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，现在我需要创建金蝶云苍穹的运维文档。让我先创建一个目录来存放这些文档，然后逐个编写。\n\n金蝶云苍穹（Kingdee Cloud）是企业级云ERP平台，我需要创建：\n1. 系统部署指南\n2. 日常运维流程\n3. 故障排查手册\n4. 性能调优方法\n5. 监控指标设置\n6. 优化建议清单\n\n让我先创建目录结构。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_b9dbcda065e34e03bea2bc2e","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /root/.openclaw/workspace-shangshu && mkdir -p docs/kingdee-cloud"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai_gongbu","model":"glm-4.7","usage":{"input":53,"output":231,"cacheRead":10817,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":11101,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773878805748}}
